            <strong>Rafi Abiyyu Airlangga</strong>, an Applied Engineering
            student of Information Science, is the brain behind the birth of
            Virtus. Starting this journey from his passion to create a
            supportive environment for artists around the world, he combined his
            technology education background as a software engineer with his
            fascination for art, especially photography and anime. With a
            passion for learning in the service of technology, he built Virtus
            single-handedly to provide an innovative platform that connects art
            and technology.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="h-full">
